{"word":"Titus","slug":"titus","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Titus</b> A Greek companion of Paul.<br/> Paul's love for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=2&verse=13'>2Co 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=7&verse=7'>2Co 7:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=7&verse=14'>2Co 7:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=23'>2Co 8:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=1&verse=4'>Tit 1:4</a><br/> With Paul in Macedonia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=7&verse=6'>2Co 7:6</a><br/> Affection of, for the Corinthians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=7&verse=15'>2Co 7:15</a><br/> Sent to Corinth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=6'>2Co 8:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=8&verse=22'>2Co 8:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=12&verse=18'>2Co 12:18</a><br/> Character of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=12&verse=18'>2Co 12:18</a><br/> Accompanies Paul to Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=3'>Gal 2:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=29'>Act 15:29</a><br/> Left by Paul in Crete<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=1&verse=5'>Tit 1:5</a><br/> To rejoin him in Nicopolis<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=3&verse=12'>Tit 3:12</a><br/> Paul writes to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=56&chapter=1&verse=4'>Tit 1:4</a><br/> With Paul in Rome<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=10'>2Ti 4:10</a><br/> Goes to Dalmatia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=10'>2Ti 4:10</a>"}]}